== 评价 ==
影片获得的评价褒贬不一。评论聚合网站[[烂番茄|烂番茄]]根据收集到的154条影评打出51%的新鲜度。网站共识指出：“《西蒙妮》的讽刺不够一针见血，剧情不足以让人相信是足够有意义的<ref>{{cite web |title = S1m0ne (2002) |url = http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/s1m0ne/ |work = Rotten Tomatoes |accessdate = 2010-07-14 |archive-date = 2020-11-27 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201127234155/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/s1m0ne |dead-url = no }}</ref>。”[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]根据38条评论打出49的平均分（满分100）<ref>{{cite web |title = Simone reviews |url = http://www.metacritic.com/video/titles/simone |work = Metacritic |accessdate = 2010-07-14 |archive-date = 2010-07-29 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20100729024651/http://www.metacritic.com/video/titles/simone |dead-url = no }}</ref>。

影片上映首周末在美国赚得3813463美元的票房，位列票房榜第九位。全球票房19576023美元<ref>{{cite web |title = Simone (2002) |url = http://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?id=simone.htm |work = Box Office Mojo |accessdate = 2010-07-14 |archive-date = 2016-08-28 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160828143541/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?id=simone.htm |dead-url = no }}</ref>。

